\id 2TI - Ekajuk New Testament
\h 2 Timoti
\toc1 2 Timoti
\toc2 2 Tim
\mt2 2 NWER NYI POL NYONO TV
\mt1 TIMOTI
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Me Pol ji li ntiingetib a Kraist Jisos, me ji koro Esowo, á yehk-m tum tib go enyam bi elkpin ni á nyame no, ni li go abo nya Kraist Jisos,
\v 2 n kpꞌnyono nwer nyia tv Timoti mmon ewame no kpo kor-m sꞌsehng.
\p Nong Esowo Nsoo, a Kraist Jisos Ntul ewahre ka-a nnoobo, a elkoono, wo fere fil-e ndon.
\s1 Ana Pol kake Timoti eltim
\p 
\v 3 Timoti, n lꞌbuum-a go egame ero bi n kpo kak atv a njul, n kpo kak Esowo saam, ye ji n kpo lok-e atahng emame saang ana babnsoo jo lim.\f + \fr 1:3 \ft Elt 23:1; 24:16\f*
\v 4 N kpꞌbuumu ana a jolo ndon ndon, a abonngo go amahr. Owo wahnge n kpꞌsahb sꞌseb re me n tiki ba nyehn-a, eji eyebatahng lꞌsahb gbal-m gbal go egame atahng.
\p 
\v 5 Me m buumu etingitingi ekakesehk ji a kpi no, elkohn ekakesehk jꞌnehm o ji nne no nkul bele no, no bo jo lung-e re Lois, jꞌnehm o ji nne Yunis tob bel.\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Elt 16:1\f* N kpꞌkahne re, elkohn nꞌnehm ni a kpi no.
\p 
\v 6 Ano wo wahnge n kp-a kpeke buumu re, wo ko ayare nya Esowo ka-a no, nya wob-a go ega atahng, jo lim eltum, kꞌbum na bum, ayare nya a bele no eji n kun-a ebo ebame.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft 1 Tim 4:14\f*
\v 7 Tibre Esowo wahr kaam etohko jio ji elfahle. Á ka-r etohko ji nsahm, ji li etohko ji elkoro, ji kpo lim-r, e fere jo mal bob elnahre.\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Rom 8:15\f*
\p 
\v 8 Owo wahnge nobo re wo kꞌjo be ndon nyi ntianse ayiimi ka Ntul ewahre.\f + \fr 1:8 \ft Rom 1:16\f* Ka ma jo nyaare, tib eji n wob ngbekobo go ege esi. Ga nob re wo tob taame erem tib esi jio ji nnoobo etib, ana Esowo ma-a ka eko,
\v 9 Esowo bio bi ma-r tahre, fere lung-r re, wahr jol ane babe. Lohngem re eltum ni e ma lim ni wahnge á lung-r no. Á lung-r tib go ege esi, a esi ji nnoobo enye nyi á ka-r no, nyi sehnge go abo nya Kraist Jisos, njini kehm jolo.
\v 10 Anv, wahr ebnyehn nnoobo nyi Esowo, eji Kraist Jisos ntꞌtahre ewahre ma ba, ye jio ji ma tane nsahm nyi elkv.\f + \fr 1:10 \ft 1 Kor 15:55\f* Yeblennge elkpin ni li go njinanjini eji á ma-r tiingi nnoobo etib.
\p 
\v 11 Esowo ma-m yehke re me n tiingi nnoobo etib bio, fere jo bung alum enye, fere tob jo tib ane.\f + \fr 1:11 \ft Elt 9:15\f*
\v 12 Esi jio ji wahng ka, n kpꞌnyehne erem bia. N nehme be ndon go nsol nyio. Tibre n kpꞌkahne nne no m ma taame tv-e. N kpꞌsahb kꞌkahn re, á bahke ma kuuru ejum jio ji á ma-m kak go ebo tete rehng go efung bio.
\p 
\v 13 Jo toono atingitingi alum nya m ma-a tib, wo sa a eltaame nꞌnehm o, a elkoro ni li go abo nya Kraist Jisos.
\v 14 Jo kuuru anoobo nsol nya bo ma-a kak go ebo go nsahm nyio nyi Etingi Etohko ji wob-r go egahre atahng.
\p 
\v 15 A kpꞌkahne re, ane bao kpee ba lene go Esia ma-m sennge njahm kpee. Figelus abola Hermogenes tob wob go bo ellong.
\v 16 Nong, Jehova tib ndon enye go etahk Onesiforus. M-e á nyaarem. Á jo ba nkpel a nkpele, ba kak-m eltim, jol eji n wobo wob ngbekobo.
\v 17 Eji á ba rehng ga Rom, á seb-m tete, kehm-m nyehne.
\v 18 Nong, á lub fili Esowo ndon efung bio. A kpꞌsahb kꞌkahn nob nob ana á jo loko eltum go Efesus.
\c 2
\s1 Nnooba nne a nsoja no Jisos Kraist
\p 
\v 1 Mmon ewame, yiimi tꞌtahne go nnoobo nyi li go abo nya Kraist Jisos.
\v 2 Ko alum enyame nya a ma wuk go esamahr atianse gbalee, wo song tib atingitingi ane ba bahke tob mal tib ane bako.
\p 
\v 3 Tob taame, nyehn erem ana nnooba nne a nsoja no Kraist Jisos.
\v 4 Nne a nsoja awohng awohng limm, no lꞌkehme ebta nok, no bahke fere song kehme eljini nehka nehka lim, eji á kpꞌsebe re á lim ji kpꞌkoro ntubesi ewe no ko-e go eltum.
\v 5 Mbekabahl no kpo be abahl, á nehm bel eltuuru ene, sehngem re no, á be jang jang ana eljini abahl li no.
\v 6 Mbahmgbe no kpo kak eko, jo lim eltum go ege egbe, ye wo fuumu re á gbo mbang li nsol alehke nyi lohng go ege egbe.
\v 7 Jo tir bade alum nya n kpꞌbungu a, tibre Jehova bahk-a limi re, wo kahn ejum ajehng ajehng.
\p 
\v 8 Jo buumu Jisos Kraist ji nyahme go elkv, ye ji lohng go etꞌtohngo ji Devid, ana n kpo tiingi nnoobo etib ebame.\f + \fr 2:8 \ft Ell 5:5\f*
\v 9 Nnoobo etib bi n kpo tiingi bi wahnge n kpꞌnyehne erem bia, a agbekobo go abo ana ebi nne. Alum Esowo, agbekobo wobem.\f + \fr 2:9 \ft Fil 1:12-14\f*
\v 10 Esi ji ane ba Esowo ma yehke ji wahnge n kpꞌkpuumu ejum ajehng ajehng, eji bo lꞌtob bel eltahre ni li go abo nya Kraist Jisos, ni kpo jen a ellub ni li go njinanjini.
\p 
\v 11 A wo li atingitingi alum nya bungu re,
\q1 “Lꞌjol re wahr ebtob kpo a ne,
\q1 e bahke tob jol a ne go elkpin.\f + \fr 2:11 \ft Fil 3:10-11\f*
\q1 
\v 12 E lꞌjo kpuumu, e bahke tob tob-e edi afili.
\q1 E lꞌten-e, á bahke tob ten-r fvfo.\f + \fr 2:12 \ft Mat 10:33\f*
\q1 
\v 13 Jol afi e gbo na go ege a mbang,
\q1 ekakesehk ji Esowo jia, kpeke li nseenga nseenge,
\q1 tibre Esowo nehm tiki yaange.”\f + \fr 2:13 \ft Rom 3:3\f*
\s1 Nlimeltum no nno
\p 
\v 14 Buumu bo nsol nyia, wo fere tong bo go esamahr Esowo re, bo kꞌkpe lim nfaabe atemtem. Nfaabe kpehme kak nne ebo, kpo rannge na ane ba lꞌwuk.
\p 
\v 15 Jo nok, eji a lꞌjol nlimeltum no nno go esamahr bi Esowo, ana nlimeltum no kil jo be ndon, eji á kpi eltum Esowo lim. Jol nne no kpo tooro atingitingi alum nya Esowo go nseenga nseenge.\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Tait 2:7-8; Mat 13:52; Luk 12:42\f*
\p 
\v 16 Ka jo yel go ellong ane ba kpo lim egboolo nfaabe nyi ki li nyi Esowo, tibre nsol nyio nyi kpo wahng ane gbal go abiafem.
\v 17 Tibre alum ane bao li ana eyam abili, bi lꞌkehme nne yam ejang ngubjing behka, kpo tob ta yel ejang ngubjing behko. Himeneus abola Filetus, bo wob ellong ane bao fvfo.\f + \fr 2:17 \ft 1 Tim 1:20\f*
\v 18 Bo nehme kpe sehng go mbang nyi li etingitingi mbang. Bobyaange mbang nyindiki kpꞌtoono, fere bvvrv ane bandiki ntim, eji bo kpꞌtibi re elnyahme ngubjing go elkv ebsehng.\f + \fr 2:18 \ft 2 Tes 2:2-3\f*
\v 19 Nnene limm, no bahke ma yuudu nnahb ekahme nyi Esowo ma bum. Alum nyaa na abal nya, bo nyono go nnahb ekahme nyio. Nehko bungu re, “Esowo kpꞌkahne ane bao ba li babe.”\f + \fr 2:19 \ft Jon 10:14\f* Nehko bungu re, “Nong, nne awohng awohng no kpꞌlungu mbing nyi Kraist, á yake abꞌbi alimi.”
\p 
\v 20 Go egburu etahk, ajoobo nsol nyaa gbalee, ana nkpingi, nyimongo bo limi go agul, nyimongo bo limi go asilva, nsol nyimongo bo ko nti lim, nsol nyimongo bo ko ndi lim, nsol nyimongo nyi nno nyi, nsol nyimongo kpꞌsabe.\f + \fr 2:20 \ft Mat 13:24-33\f*
\p 
\v 21 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌbum elne saang, yake nsol nyi kpꞌsabe, á bahke jolo ana ekpingi ji nno, ji bo ma bum eje eje, eji nde nne lꞌjo ko, lim ejum ajehng ajehng ji nno.
\p 
\v 22 Jo jahng nsol nyi kpo melle ajangkun go bo atahng re bo jo lim. Nok, eji a lꞌli eno go esamahr Esowo, fere bel ekakesehk, a elkoro, go elkoono, wo fere woomo go ellong ane ba kpo kak ero ka Esowo a ntim ebo saang.
\p 
\v 23 Ka jo yel ellong agboolo ane ba kil kahne ejumjum, ba kpo lim nfaabe nfaabe. Tibre a kpꞌkahne re, go esꞌkohlo nfaabe nyio, ntaange nyi kpo gbo.
\v 24 Fuumem re nlokeltum no Jehova jo taange ntaange. Á bahke bele nnoobo eljini a nne awohng awohng, fere jol nne no kpo mal eltibi.\f + \fr 2:24 \ft Kol 4:6\f* Á bahke jo kpuumu, bo lꞌlim-e ebi,
\v 25 fere jo tub ane ba kpꞌlimi nfaabe a ne elle go enange bem. Fundiki Esowo bahke limi mbang ka bo, bo gbo ndon go bo abiafem, fere kahn etingitingi,
\v 26 eji bo lꞌlohng go ekpoko bi nnehm nyi ma bob bo re bo jo lim ji kp-e koro.
\c 3
\s1 Esꞌkohro afung
\p 
\v 1 Jo kahne re, ngare esꞌkohro afung bahke jolo etahntahn ngare.\f + \fr 3:1 \ft 1 Tim 4:1\f*
\v 2 Ane bahke jo tiiri elbo elbo, fere jo baare amahr akpohko, jo wor anyo, fere jo lim agabbe, jo su ane. Bo nehm jo wuk babnde ebo, saam bo nehm jo kak. Esowo nehm jo lub bo.
\v 3 Elkoro anehng anehng bo nehm bel. Bo nehm jo tahm ka ane. Bo bahke jo kiimi afahnge lake ane. Ndon bo nehm bel. Bo bahke jo lim nsol, bo nehm jo feere njahm. Elyebe ni njini bahke jo kor bo. Esowo nehm jo kor bo.
\v 4 Bo bahke jo bel atem go nnyo a nnyo. Bo bahke jo lim nsol go elrang elrang. Bo bahke jolo ane ba bahke jo rod elbo wahre wahre. Bo bahke jo lim ana ji kpꞌkoro bofono antahng. Esowo nehm jo kor bo.
\v 5 Eljini ni bo, bahke jo foongo ni aneb Esowo, jol nsahm nyi bo, bo nehm bel.\f + \fr 3:5 \ft Mat 7:15,21\f* Ka jo yel ellong ane bao!
\p 
\v 6 Egom ane bao bandiki bahke jo kpaale yannge go etahk ajehng ajehng, song kpiri agboolo anebkal ba ma gbal go abꞌbi, bao ba ajoobo nsol kpo melle bo go bo atahng, eji bo lꞌko bo elfono.
\v 7 Bo kpo kpili na kpili kpili kpili, jol bo nehm tiki kahn etingitingi.
\p 
\v 8 Ana Jannes abola Jambres jo ten Moses, ano wo fvfo ane bao ba kil elkpe ga tir nob nob kpo tob ten etingitingi. Bobgbo go mbang nyi Esowo.
\v 9 Ekidi nehm ga lab, nne awohng awohng bahke nyehne agboolo nsol nya bo kpo lim, jang jang ana ane nyehne goji Jannes a Jambres.
\s1 Eljini ni nne Esowo bahke jo lim, kehm jo gbal
\p 
\v 10 Wo Timoti, wobwuk eltibi ename, fere nyehn eljini ename. A kpꞌkahne ji wahnge n kpi elkpin ana nia. A nyꞌnyehn ekakesehk ejame, fere nyehn ana n jolo soom. A nyꞌnyehn elkoro ename, fere nyehn ana n jo kpuumu.
\v 11 A nyꞌnyehn ana bo jo gbak-m, fere nyehn ana n jo nyehn erem go Antiok, a Ikonium, go Listra, fere nyehn ana n kpuumu elgbake nio kpee. Jehova ma-m tahre yehke go nsol nyio kpee.\f + \fr 3:11 \ft Elt 13:50; 14:5,19\f*
\p 
\v 12 Nne awohng awohng no lꞌtong re á bahke toono Kraist Jisos, fere jo lim eljini ni Esowo, á bahke tiki jo nyehn erem bi ane bahke jo gbak-e.\f + \fr 3:12 \ft Elt 14:22\f*
\v 13 Abi ane, a ane ba kpo nehm ane, bo kpꞌsoro asi go abꞌbi alimi sehnge ana wuku wuku. Bo kpo nehm ane bako, fere tob nehm elbo.
\p 
\v 14 Timoti, soro asi, wo jo lim nsol nyi a ma kpili, fere taame tv, eji a kpꞌkahne nne no tib-a no.
\v 15 A bomo nwer Esowo akahne ngare nyi a jolo ntiil tete sik anv. Nwer nyio bahk-a ma ka elkahne ni a bahke kahne mbang nyi eltahre.\f + \fr 3:15 \ft Jon 5:39\f* Eltahre nio li go abo nya Kraist Jisos.
\p 
\v 16 Alum Esowo kpee lohng goji Esowo,\f + \fr 3:16 \ft 2 Pit 1:19-21\f* eji lꞌlim nnoobo ka ane. Alum Esowo kpo tib etingitingi, fere jo nyam ane, jo soongo bo, fere jo rehke bo re bo jol go etingitingi,
\v 17 eji nne Esowo lꞌjol nob nob, fere jo mal ellimi eltum anehng anehng ni nno.
\c 4
\s1 Ana Pol jo rehke Timoti
\p 
\v 1 Erehke ji n kp-a kake a, n kp-a kake go esamahr bi Esowo, a bi Jisos Kraist, ye ji bahke lame aneb mbir mbir, a ba ma kpo. Tib go elbake ene ni á bahke bake ba ji go ege a nji etul, owo wahnge n kp-a tongo re,
\v 2 wo jo bung alum Esowo, kꞌjo be ndon, afi jolo ngare anyi.\f + \fr 4:2 \ft Elt 20:20,31\f* Jo lennge abiafem tong bo, wo fere jo nyam bo, fere jo rehke bo. Lim nsol nyia kpee go mbang nyi a kpꞌtibi na bo, a elkpuumu.
\p 
\v 3 Tibre ngare kpꞌbake nyi ane lꞌkꞌkpe jo kor bo re bo jo wuungu atung go etingitingi eltibi. Bo bahke jo toono ana ji bo bahke jo tir go bo a ntim. Bo bahke jo lim elbo, eji bo bahke jo seb atꞌtibi ba bahke jo tib bo nsol nyi bahke jo yebe bo go atung.
\v 4 Bo bahke sennge etingitingi njahm, fere jo wuungu atung go aka nya li ana amongo.\f + \fr 4:4 \ft 2 Tes 2:11\f*
\v 5 Wo, jo kunu elna ekpu go ejum ajehng ajehng! Jo kpuumu erem, wo fere jo lim eltum ni alum Esowo abungu. Jo lim eltum ena nseenga nseenge!
\p 
\v 6 Tibre afung nya m bahke tahme njini nyia sa ebbiingi. Bo ma-m rod kpꞌyaange wohng go ana alahb njom ma Esowo, ma bo kpo yaange wohng go.\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Fil 2:17\f*
\v 7 Me n nok ebta ebame go mbang nyi nno. Me n gohro be abahl enyame. Me m bel ekakesehk go eltoono mbang nyi Esowo.
\v 8 Anv, ekpasi eltuuru jia, nong-m go esꞌsong, ekpasi jio ji eno ji Esowo bi li nnooba nlamalam bahk-m tuuru efung bio. Me ntahngtahng sang á bahk-m tuuru. Á bahke tob tuuru nne awohng awohng no elbake ni á bahke bake kp-e koro.\f + \fr 4:8 \ft 1 Pit 5:4; Jems 1:12; Ell 2:10\f*
\s1 Alum nya Pol gohro bung
\p 
\v 9 Lim, wo gulu elbake ga egame.
\v 10 Tibre Demas, njini nyia m-e kehme elkoro.\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Kol 4:14\f* Á ma-m tahm sa, tahm eje go Tesalonaika. Kresens ebtahm go Galesa. Taitus ebtahm go Dalmesa.
\v 11 Luk ntahngtahng wo ma sa a name. Ko Mak, wo ba a ne, tibre á bahk-m ma kak ebo go eltum.\f + \fr 4:11 \ft Elt 15:37; Kol 4:10\f*
\v 12 Me n tum Tikikus tv go Efesus.\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Elt 20:4; Ef 6:21; Kol 4:7\f*
\p 
\v 13 A lꞌkehm bake, soro ko ekpawobo ejame ji n tahme sa go etahk nsoo Karpus go Troas, ba ka-m. Tob ko awer enyame ba a nya, asehngesehnge awer nya n kpo nyon nsol.
\p 
\v 14 Aleksanda ntahletahl lim-m egburu ebi sehng.\f + \fr 4:14 \ft 1 Tim 1:20\f* Esowo bahk-e bongo jang jang ana á limi no.
\v 15 Wofono antahng, jo kun-e ekpu, tibre á tohkem tꞌtaame tv alum enyahre nya e jo bung.
\p 
\v 16 Go egame elam, eji n gbo mbang tooro nnyo elam emame, nnene jolem no yiim-m njahm. Bo kpee yaam-m sa.\f + \fr 4:16 \ft 2 Tim 1:15\f* Nong, Esowo lub tahm ka bo.
\v 17 Esowo bi yiim-m njahm, fere ka-m eko, eji etib ebame lꞌyiimi, ane baka baka ba ki nyi Esowo lꞌwuk. Ano wo wahnge á tahr-m no yehke go nnyo mi egabe.\f + \fr 4:17 \ft Elt 23:11; 27:23-24\f*
\p 
\v 18 Esowo bahk-m tahre yehke go nfem anyehng anyehng, fere kp-m tahm a name go ejahbetul eje. Nong, ellub jol a ne go njinanjini. Emen.
\s1 Nnyo mi Pol gohro kak
\p 
\v 19 Kak Priska abola Akwila nnyo,\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Elt 18:2; Rom 16:3\f* wo fere kak Onesiforus nnyo, a aneb etahk ebe.
\v 20 Erastus sa go Korint.\f + \fr 4:20 \ft Elt 19:22\f* Trofimus, n tahm-e sa go Miletus, á kpꞌyame.\f + \fr 4:20 \ft Elt 20:4; 21:29\f*
\p 
\v 21 Lim, wo ba ga egame, elkoko kehm rehnge. Yubulus, Pudens, Lenus, a Klodia, bo kpee tong-m re me n kak-a nnyo. Abon Esowo bako go tob tong-m re me n kak-a nnyo.
\p 
\v 22 Nong, Esowo jol a etohko eja. Nnoobo nyi Esowo jol a na. Emen.
